info.name: Harley Quinn logo to replace tumblr logo
info.description: Replace the "tumblr." logo on the top left of your dashboard with a Harley Quinn logo

style.css: @-moz-document url-prefix('http://www.tumblr.com/'), url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com/')   { #logo {height: 0 !important; width: 0 !important; padding-left: 350px !important; padding-top: 44px !important; background: url(http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mahba69WTT1qc0er4.png) no-repeat !important;}}
